# Kconfig for test_app_audio

config TEST_APP_AUDIO_PSRAM_TESTS
    bool "Enable on-device PSRAM integration tests"
    default SPIRAM
    help
      Enable the PSRAM integration tests which exercise heap_caps and
      audio_processor allocations that prefer PSRAM. This option defaults to
      the value of SPIRAM (enabled when SPIRAM is enabled in project config).

      If disabled, the PSRAM integration tests will be skipped and the
      test runner will print a clear skip message.
